3.6.1. Harris Hematoxylin and Congo Red Place the fixed slide in acidified Harris Hematoxylin for 5 min. Wash under gently running tapwater until blued. Place in Congo Red and stain for 15 min. Wash briefly under gently running tapwater and dry. Nuclei stain blue, eosinophil granules red. Blue

